varValue.code:
const formData = context.local.data?.['form']?.['fields'] || {};
return {
  productName: formData.productName?.value,
  companyName: formData.companyName?.value,
  price: parseFloat(formData.price?.value),
  commission: parseFloat(formData.commission?.value),
  paymentMethods: formData.paymentMethods?.value,
  category: formData.category?.value,
  subcategory: formData.subcategory?.value,
  description: formData.description?.value
}
